<D>__{i was doing the lambada with her and the guy freaks, he breaks my arm, tries to kill me. i swear man, the guy thought i was a piata. if nobody else hadn't a been there, he wouldn't have stopped. he woulda killed me. fuckin' guy man, just snapped. how do you like your burger?}
