<D>__{...and one, and two, and yes, i am. but no one gets them working like junior used to...and two, and one.. they call him the 'quasimodo of the lanes.' he's the best pinman there is.. and one and two...people used to say he got the machines working so well 'cause he lubricated them with blood...and two, and one...but people just love saying things about junior.}
